installation.excerpt: Pretrained SqueezeNext models on ImageNet have been added to imgclsmob repository. In Pytorch you can use the following command to load the pretrained network:

invocation.excerpt:
from pytorchcv.model_provider import get_model as ptcv_get_model 
net = ptcv_get_model(“sqnxt23_w1”, pretrained=True)
